<main><div class="innerpage"><div class="main-product-banner"><img src="assets/images/activa-125-bs6/activa-125Landing-Page.gif"s class="resposive-img"></div><div class="about-product"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-6"><div class="about-left"><h2>Activa 125 BS-VI</h2><p>Innovation. Disruption. Being the first-of-a-kind. That’s starting a revolution. But we took it a step further and started... A Quiet Revolution.</p><p>Presenting the new Activa 125 BS-VI with Honda’s globally acclaimed Enhanced Smart Power (eSP) technology and many first in segment features. The eSP technology combines high power and high fuel efficiency with a quiet start, and a smooth eco-friendly engine. It also helps deliver a 13% increase in mileage and is integrated with the ACG starter motor to start the engine jolt free. With the highly efficient and advanced 125cc HET BS-VI engine, it is sure to silence all doubts about an unmatched performance by delivering consistent power output and higher mileage.The Idling Stop System automatically switches the engine off at traffic lights and other brief stops to save fuel.</p><p>The revolutionary “Side Stand Engine Cut Off” stops the engine start when the side stand is engaged. The intelligent digital analog meter displays advanced information like distance to empty, average and real time mileage. No need to dismount for refuelling on the Activa 125 BS-VI with the external fuel fill which works with just a flip of the first in segment multi-function switch. The premium chrome on the sides, broader chrome chest in the front, the LED headlamp and Signature LED position lamp adds a premium style to it. The Activa 125 BS-VI comes with first in segment 6 years warranty package which includes 3 years standard and 3 years optional warranty. The all new Activa 125 BS-VI is set to revolutionize the segment by setting highest standards in technology, innovation, reliability, comfort and style.</p><p>Welcome to A Quiet Revolution.</p><div class="price"id="